title: Police Officer with Patrol Cars in Kent
description: A police officer walks towards a row of parked patrol cars in a parking lot at night in Kent, Washington. The cars are marked with city emblems and emergency lights, with one vehicle bearing the number 358 on the front. The scene is illuminated by streetlights and surrounded by trees and a brick wall. The reverse side of the image is annotated with 'Kent, WA' and includes a newspaper clipping about law enforcement efforts and a date stamp of October 21, 1987.
